and components; retail; food processing; agribusiness; insurance; textiles; and mill products industries. The company was formerly known as Sphere Global Services Limited and changed its name to Adroit Infotech Limited in February 2018. Adroit Infotech Limited was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Hyderabad, India."}}